2023-05-16

1 - Click in “Browse”

2 - Load the csv file containing the Historical data.

Important

The layout of this document must be:

1st column - SKU code

2nd column - Demand

3rd column - Period in a text format “YYYY-MM”.

3 - After loaded, you may see a table with the loaded data

4 - In the field “SKU” inform the desired sku.

5 - In the tab “Model” you will see the chosen model. In the example (an item with seasonal and trend pattern) the model chosen was an seasonal AR(1) with 1 lag of displacement I(1)

Caption for the picture.

6 - In the tab “Residuals” you will see the residual analysis.
